import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  import { Playground,PropsTable } from 'docz'
import { Button, Icon } from 'antd'

export default ({components, ...props}) => <MDXTag name="wrapper"  components={components}>
<MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"button"}}>{`Button`}</MDXTag>
<PropsTable of={Button} />
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"basic-usage"}}>{`Basic usage`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={1} __code={`<Button type="primary">Click me</Button>
<Button type="primary" icon="search">
  Search
</Button>
<Button>Click me</Button>
<Button type="primary">
  <Icon type="left" />
  Go back
</Button>`} __scope={{props,Button,Icon}}>
  <Button type="primary">Click me</Button>
  <Button type="primary" icon="search">Search</Button>
  <Button>Click me</Button>
  <Button type="primary">
    <Icon type="left" />Go back
  </Button>
</Playground></MDXTag>
